{"tid":144632,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【處境題】係港鐵同廢老爭座位⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-03-05T14:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T15:49:28.000Z","uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be096d6284da72dc74d12650cab081fbfd2dbe2b","tid":144632,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"放工時段，你番屋企，特別去總站搭車，希望有位坐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知成架車得番一個位，同時間有個廢老婆婆九秒九衝緊過黎，你本能反應即刻坐落去理撚得佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢人一步既廢老面有不甘，企係你面前施壓，但當你完全無諗過讓坐既期間，先發現屁股一濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來個座濕左先無人坐<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n如何不失霸氣⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599c6a040ebe16993878616265046793538db3d0","tid":144632,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/41/98/qJeZn5_WlKKcrKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F41%2F98%2FqJeZn5_WlKKcrKQ.jpg&h=02d45f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f8eedba1093578844dc59b824ef62b3ff4a329e","tid":144632,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9L1062c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9L1062c.jpg&h=eba1ab78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a8dee202136220d0b6273eecc374bc4b859c78b","tid":144632,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUjHGqhPppk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgUjHGqhPppk&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ5zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=cfab69b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gUjHGqhPppk</a>"},{"pid":"9370e3b79fc48010862b651e44705fedbdae1538